node.text:
There’s a few reasons why you are NOT going to sell anything. Stop wasting your time and make a quick evaluation of these few things.

1. YOUR OFFER- ok, I know this might break your heart or crush your ego to hear...but your offer might not be good. If there is not a demand for your product or service it doesn’t matter how skilled your marketing is. It won’t sell! Your opinion means nothing...the market will tell you if there’s a demand or not.

2. YOUR ADS- Look, it’s more than just pushing that shiny PROMOTE button beneath your post. There is a science, a psychology and an art to good ads. 
A lot of people waste a lot of money trying to “play around” with ads. Don’t be that person...leave it to the experts if you really want to make money.

3. YOUR LANDING PAGE- This is where you are sending the traffic. You can have an awesome offer, perfect ad but if your landing page is not good...well it’s like having a brand new Lamborghini with a full tank of gas...but you don’t have the KEY.
Yes, your landing page is the key to conversions.

🔥 Here's 3 secrets that allowed me to manage over $500 Million (For Our Clients including people like Tai Lopez, Grant Cardone, Fortune 500 companies, A-List Celebrities and more) in ad spend online, and help build some of the largest online businesses that you probably know of today.

Secret 1️⃣: Learn how to COMBINE social media with paid traffic.  This is HUGE.  I've seen so many social media gurus that teach you how to put out content, use the right hashtags, network with people, etc.  But they can't seem to ever tap into putting their offers in front of millions of people.
Learn how to fuel a good social media strategy with paid traffic.  When you learn to build large audiences, you have massive leverage.  By the way, right now our favorite traffic source is doing paid ads with messenger bots.

Secret 2️⃣: Funnels.  No matter what anyone says, they work...if you have an actual offer that the market place wants.  Focus on learning to master 1 or 2 funnel concepts and you are on your way to building a massive business.  For us there are 2 funnels that we focus on.
ONE is the webinar funnel.  Our webinar funnels continue to churn out millions of dollars per year, and we use the exact same formula for building every webinar. TWO is the Tripwire funnel.  We use these funnels to bring in thousands of new customers into our world every month.  Learn these 2 funnel concepts and your business can change almost overnight.

Secret 3️⃣: High Ticket Offers.  No matter what kind of funnel you use in your business, you need some kind of a high ticket offer to truly be able to leverage paid traffic.  If you don't currently have a high ticket offer, don't be discouraged.  It's usually not near as hard to put together a high ticket offer as you might think.
Put these 3 things together in your business and watch your business take off!

node.text:
“𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐝𝐨𝐧’𝐭 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝 𝐚 𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫…”

Has never been said by any successful person. The facts are, we all need mentors. 

Here’s a few reasons why:

1. 𝐀 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐂𝐚𝐧 𝐏𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐭 𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐑𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 - Every business has holes and opportunities and areas that need improvement. A good mentor can help you find those and Fox them quickly.

2. 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐁𝐞𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐧 𝐁𝐨𝐨𝐤𝐬- Yes, we all know reeding books are good for you! Yes, I know I spelled that wrong. But mentors are gooder than books…yeah, I did it again. Mentors talk to you…they answer questions and do more than set on shelves and collect dust.

3. 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐖𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐓𝐞𝐚𝐜𝐡 𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐅𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐬𝐭 𝐌𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐤𝐞𝐬- you don’t need to make all the mistakes. Working with a mentor will help you save a lot of time, trouble and mistakes. Learn from their experiences.

4. 𝐇𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐎𝐟 𝐒𝐮𝐜𝐜𝐞𝐬𝐬 - one statistic says that people are 10x more likely to succeed with a mentor. Not sure where that statistic comes from…but it sounds good and makes sense. 

5. 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐂𝐚𝐧 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐜𝐭 𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐑𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭 𝐏𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞 - Like the over-used meme always says “Your network is your net worth “ A good mentor can make life-changing introductions that can help you in life.

6. 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐂𝐚𝐧 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐯𝐢𝐝𝐞 𝐄𝐧𝐜𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐚𝐠𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭-
Outside of all the invaluable knowledge a mentor can bring…it’s also good to have someone on your side rooting you on! You can do it!

🛑STOP JUDGING YOURSELF WITH OTHERS🛑

It is a dangerous thing to do…everyone is at different chapters in their life. 
It can be both discouraging and misleading to judge yourself only based on what you see others are doing.

Most of the time you don’t know all their story or the full details of where they truly are.

LOOK IN THE MIRROR…that is your biggest competition.

Strive to be a better person each and every day.

DO YOU AGREE?

Don’t let anybody tell you that you can’t do it!

4. Livestream- allows you to watch and also stream events online. Great quality and great content.

6. Short Reckonings- a great way to easily track your shared expenses. Simple to use for everyone.

7. Privnote- send private notes that self-destruct after they are read. The James Bond online self-destructing messages.
